WEBVTT

00:07:59.629 --> 00:08:01.788
And this metaphor in my head --

00:08:01.812 --> 00:08:04.553
I've got anagnorisis
and peripeteia on my chin --

00:08:04.577 --> 00:08:06.842
(Laughter)

00:08:06.866 --> 00:08:09.470
I've got to tell you,
it's such a great device, though.

00:08:09.494 --> 00:08:12.067
When you start to look for peripeteia,

00:08:12.091 --> 00:08:13.628
you find it everywhere.

00:08:13.652 --> 00:08:16.565
I mean, Bruce Willis
in "The Sixth Sense," right?

00:08:16.589 --> 00:08:20.145
Spends the whole movie trying to help
the little kid who sees dead people,

00:08:20.169 --> 00:08:21.894
and then -- boom! -- "Oh, I'm dead."

00:08:21.918 --> 00:08:23.078
Peripeteia. You know?

00:08:23.102 --> 00:08:26.572
It's crushing when the audience
sees it the right way.

00:08:26.596 --> 00:08:29.097
Neo in "The Matrix," you know?

00:08:29.121 --> 00:08:31.096
"Oh, I'm living in a computer program.